Lake has excessive amount of water meal and duck weed.   If there is no wind- the surface is completely green...wind moves it to one side.    Lake has suspended "chunks" of algae that are as big as a basketball and bright green  Lake is clear... visibility good.   Excessive amounts of milfoil and coontail.....worst in years.
